{"tid":2165736,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不滿警暴網上撐獨立調查 入境處人員被清算降級","createTime":"2020-08-20T04:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T13:33:22.000Z","uid":241764,"like":6,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ae7be15c2847dea14325317539d9d89c17a05bc3","tid":2165736,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T04:23:11.000Z","msg":"「反送中」運動以來，林鄭政府要求公務員盲目效忠，員工之間亦掀起一場「白色恐怖」。《蘋果》獲悉，一名署任入境事務主任疑因網上言論，遭上司「照肺」，更在原訂正式坐正前3個月被降回原來的入境事務助理員職級。新公務員工會主席顏武周確認，接獲多名公務員因網上言論被截圖而遭到投訴的求助，不少同事已將社交賬戶改名或轉為私人賬戶。<br />\n<br />\n再有公務員因網上言論遭當局打壓。《蘋果》獲悉，一名黃姓入境處人員，原屬入境事務助理員職級，早前通過內部考核後升職，獲安排署任入境事務主任，原訂約2至3個月後即坐滿3年署任期，正式擔任入境事務主任。<br />\n<br />\n惟該名入境處人員疑因在「反送中」運動期間在網上發表支持成立獨立調查委員會言論，以及對有紀律部隊人員濫用武力和不出示委任證等表達不滿。據了解，有人將相關留言截圖並作投訴，入境處近日正式取消該名入境處人員的署任安排，將其由署任入境事務主任位置降回至入境事務助理員職級。<br />\n<br />\n全文: <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/CNXWHQO4BFGDLFT3EJKIXKVGJQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1DvOQ6u28JiI8p4jMEBK0ybEiTwWteCEuYjFiFK6_NRtrUPSbrsk0kBgo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2FCNXWHQO4BFGDLFT3EJKIXKVGJQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1DvOQ6u28JiI8p4jMEBK0ybEiTwWteCEuYjFiFK6_NRtrUPSbrsk0kBgo&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufRQiWlS3rEx2Iifn9b7K3wo%3D&h=6bb40f4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2FCNXWHQO4BFGDLFT3EJKIXKVGJQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1DvOQ6u28JiI8p4jMEBK0ybEiTwWteCEuYjFiFK6_NRtrUPSbrsk0kBgo&h=94bc0d3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/CNXWHQO4BFGDLFT3EJKIXKVGJQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1DvOQ6u